Dad, I think I sprained my ankle.

55
00:05:09,649 --> 00:05:11,519
- I'll take Eun Sol.
- Dad.

56
00:05:11,579 --> 00:05:14,089
- Hyun Mi, you go first. Go on.
- Dad.

57
00:05:14,149 --> 00:05:15,449
Hurry and go.

58
