That crazy jerk
is trying to kill everyone in here.

62
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:16,680
- Mr. Choi.
- Let go of me.

63
00:06:16,980 --> 00:06:18,250
I have to save the people out there.

64
00:06:18,319 --> 00:06:21,389
Monsters are swarming all over.
Why would you open the door?

65
00:06:21,449 --> 00:06:25,060
Sir, people and our students
are out there.

66
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:28,790
Chairman Choi told me
never to open the door.

67
00:06:29,459 --> 00:06:30,459
What?

68
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:33,430
- Mr. Choi.
- Hyun Mi.

69
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:36,470
Hyun Mi, Hyun Mi!

70
00:06:36,529 --> 00:06:39,199
No, no, no. Hyun Mi!

71
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,009
Hyun Mi!

72
00:06:41,170 --> 00:06:44,410
Hyun Mi! Hyun Mi! No!

73
00:06:57,790 --> 00:06:58,790
See?

74
00:06:59,259 --> 00:07:01,560
Will you still
follow Chairman Choi's order?

75
00:07:02,230 --> 00:07:06,000
Would you have done the same
if she were your daughter?

76
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:07,529
Kid.

77
00:08:10,459 --> 00:08:11,459
Kid?

78
00:08:15,230 --> 00:08:16,230
Where are you?

79
00:08:35,149 --> 00:08:37,460
Maybe it doesn't affect animals.

80
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:08,019
Come inside. Hurry.

81
00:09:14,429 --> 00:09:15,460
Are you all right?

82
00:09:17,460 --> 00:09:18,659
Thank you.

83
00:09:20,700 --> 00:09:23,700
Have you seen a child coming in here?

84
00:09:23,769 --> 00:09:24,899
It's a little girl.

85
00:09:25,669 --> 00:09:27,639
Are you looking for Do Yoon?

86
00:09:28,269 --> 00:09:29,509
Do you know her?

87
00:09:30,470 --> 00:09:31,909
Detective.

88
00:09:45,389 --> 00:09:47,259
Are you okay, Detective?

89
00:09:47,730 --> 00:09:50,230
If you're hurt, I can take a look at it.

90
00:09:53,460 --> 00:09:57,269
No, I'm fine. I just bumped
into an injured person on the street.

91
00:09:57,769 --> 00:10:01,169
Why did you take the girl with you?

92
00:10:02,110 --> 00:10:04,840
I think there is a misunderstanding.

93
00:10:05,509 --> 00:10:07,879
I saw Do Yoon on the street
alone in danger.

94
00:10:07,950 --> 00:10:09,379
That's why I took her.

95
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:13,779
Do you know this girl?

96
00:10:14,350 --> 00:10:18,620
Yes. I work with Do Yoon's mom
at the hospital as a nurse.

97
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:23,789
So are you a detective?

98
00:10:25,129 --> 00:10:28,230
I'm from Seoul. I'm a detective
of the Regional Investigation Unit.

99
00:10:30,700 --> 00:10:32,970
Why did you come
all the way down here from Seoul?

100
00:10:33,539 --> 00:10:35,269
I was looking for someone.

101
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:39,980
I see. Were you tracking down
a criminal by any chance?

102
00:10:42,710 --> 00:10:46,279
But where is Do Yoon's mother?

103
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:54,590
She died.

104
00:11:01,299 --> 00:11:02,299
Do Yoon.

105
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:04,200
It's okay.

106
00:11:05,070 --> 00:11:07,909
You're going to stay here with me.

107
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:17,350
Sister, could you bring Do Yoon
something to drink?

108
00:11:17,419 --> 00:11:18,519
Yes, Disciple.

109
00:11:18,980 --> 00:11:20,919
We have some hot chocolate.
Would you like to have some?

110
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:26,559
You don't need my permission.

111
00:11:28,029 --> 00:11:29,029
Okay.

112
00:11:35,269 --> 00:11:36,870
Is it because you're a detective?

113
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:40,970
How could you say that her mother is dead
right in front of her?

114
00:11:43,139 --> 00:11:45,580
Because she needs to be stronger now.

115
00:12:02,889 --> 00:12:04,100
What is this place?

116
00:12:07,769 --> 00:12:08,970
Don't be afraid.

117
00:12:09,830 --> 00:12:12,669
This is the place where the New Lord is.

118
00:12:41,269 --> 00:12:42,600
Are you all right?

119
00:12:45,370 --> 00:12:46,370
Yes.

120
00:12:47,039 --> 00:12:48,309
What is it?

121
00:12:48,669 --> 00:12:52,210
This belongs to one of the sisters.

122
00:12:52,279 --> 00:12:55,009
I thought it'd be better
than your bloodstained clothes.

123
00:12:57,179 --> 00:12:58,419
Thank you.

124
00:12:59,019 --> 00:13:00,750
Are you sure you're okay?

125
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,320
Excuse me?

126
00:13:03,590 --> 00:13:05,860
You haven't been looking very well.

127
00:13:06,490 --> 00:13:08,559
Would you like to drink the water of life?

128
00:13:11,330 --> 00:13:14,899
It will calm your nerves down.

129
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:18,970
No thanks. I'll be fine.

130
00:13:22,639 --> 00:13:23,970
You know what?

131
00:13:24,879 --> 00:13:27,309
You and Do Yoon came here...

132
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:29,580
because you were
guided here by the New Lord.

133
00:13:31,049 --> 00:13:32,419
The New Lord is...

134
00:13:33,049 --> 00:13:35,950
punishing the ones without faith.

135
00:13:37,389 --> 00:13:38,720
What do you mean?

136
00:13:38,820 --> 00:13:41,330
The New Lord guided you here.

137
00:13:41,629 --> 00:13:43,090
So you should have faith in him too.

138
00:13:46,759 --> 00:13:48,669
Are you serious?

139
00:13:51,070 --> 00:13:53,200
Your eyes are full of doubt.

140
00:13:54,539 --> 00:13:56,940
You have to banish the doubt
so you can get on the ship of salvation...

141
00:13:57,009 --> 00:13:58,139
Listen to me.

142
00:13:59,039 --> 00:14:01,409
You can have faith in whatever you want.

143
00:14:02,480 --> 00:14:04,220
But you have to get it together.

144
00:14:04,919 --> 00:14:06,919
Because that's the only way to survive.

145
00:14:10,549 --> 00:14:11,659
What about Do Yoon?

146
00:14:13,419 --> 00:14:16,490
You're free to choose your own destiny.

147
00:14:17,029 --> 00:14:19,830
But you don't have the right
to choose what's good for Do Yoon.

148
00:14:21,429 --> 00:14:22,529
Do Yoon...

149
00:14:23,230 --> 00:14:25,870
is safer here with me.

150
00:14:27,639 --> 00:14:29,039
Think about it.

151
00:15:28,129 --> 00:15:31,269
Please help me!

152
00:15:32,570 --> 00:15:35,240
Help me!

153
00:15:36,340 --> 00:15:37,370
Please...

154
00:15:40,980 --> 00:15:42,850
Thank you.

155
00:15:50,649 --> 00:15:53,559
(Muji-daero)

156
00:15:56,590 --> 00:15:59,830
Help me.

157
00:16:09,470 --> 00:16:12,039
(Taehan Towing)

158
00:16:12,279 --> 00:16:14,980
(Muji Hospital, 2km)

159
00:16:47,379 --> 00:16:49,950
Thank you for your hard work.

160
00:16:55,620 --> 00:17:00,419
Doctor, this should be enough
to block out the black smoke, right?

161
00:17:00,490 --> 00:17:04,599
Yes. The door is triple-layered,
so the smoke won't be able to get in.

162
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:07,130
But I'm not sure about the infected.

163
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:10,799
But Officer Cho and I are here,
so don't worry too much.

164
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:13,769
Everyone, please rest assured.

165
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:16,009
A rescue team will arrive soon.

166
00:17:16,069 --> 00:17:17,470
- Thank goodness!
- We're safe!

167
00:17:17,539 --> 00:17:21,579
Officer Park! Officer Park!

168
00:17:21,650 --> 00:17:22,980
Officer Park!

169
00:17:23,049 --> 00:17:26,420
Officer Park, thank you so much
for your help.

170
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:27,890
Please have a cup of coffee.

171
00:17:27,950 --> 00:17:29,289
Thank you.

172
00:17:29,589 --> 00:17:32,890
Officer Park, you're amazing.

173
00:17:34,089 --> 00:17:36,660
You risk your life for the people...

174
00:17:36,730 --> 00:17:38,430
and carry the ball.

175
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:40,359
Everyone.

176
00:17:41,670 --> 00:17:43,230
All we have to do now...

177
00:17:43,769 --> 00:17:46,470
is just trust Officer Park.

178
00:17:46,869 --> 00:17:48,970
- Of course!
- We trust you!

179
00:17:49,369 --> 00:17:51,309
Great work today.

180
00:17:54,140 --> 00:17:55,779
He's so reliable.

181
00:17:56,079 --> 00:17:58,880
Yes, he is.

182
00:18:02,450 --> 00:18:04,859
The number you've reached
is not available.

183
00:18:11,029 --> 00:18:12,430
Can you still not reach her?

184
00:18:12,730 --> 00:18:13,730
No.

185
00:18:14,500 --> 00:18:17,000
I'm sure the line will be restored soon.
Don't worry so much.

186
00:18:34,990 --> 00:18:39,490
(Taehan Towing)

187
00:20:10,980 --> 00:20:12,150
What was that?

188
00:20:13,650 --> 00:20:16,589
(Police)

189
00:20:35,470 --> 00:20:38,279
Hey, open the door!

190
00:20:38,339 --> 00:20:41,180
Please open the door!

191
00:20:41,240 --> 00:20:42,349
Hey!

192
00:20:43,950 --> 00:20:46,019
(Muji Hospital)

193
00:20:47,049 --> 00:20:49,490
Soon Il. It's me, Tae Han!

194
00:20:49,589 --> 00:20:51,089
Open the door!

195
00:20:51,150 --> 00:20:53,059
There's an emergency patient here!

196
00:20:53,119 --> 00:20:54,730
Open the door quickly!

197
00:20:54,759 --> 00:20:57,130
He needs help urgently! What're you doing?

198
00:20:57,190 --> 00:20:58,700
Things are getting interesting.

199
00:20:58,759 --> 00:21:00,130
Doctor!

200
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:02,470
There's an emergency patient here.
Please open the door!

201
00:21:02,529 --> 00:21:05,500
Officer Park,
why aren't you opening the door?

202
00:21:05,970 --> 00:21:07,640
- Okay.
- Wait!

203
00:21:08,369 --> 00:21:10,539
We need to prioritize the safety
of the people inside.

204
00:21:10,609 --> 00:21:13,279
If he's infected,
all of us will be in danger!

205
00:21:13,339 --> 00:21:15,650
I said open the door!

206
00:21:25,660 --> 00:21:28,089
Soon Il! Soon Il!

207
00:21:34,599 --> 00:21:35,930
Are you crazy?

208
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:38,339
- I'm really going to break it!
- Officer Park!

209
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:40,740
We can't let the smoke get in.
Open the door right now!

210
00:21:40,799 --> 00:21:43,470
I'll do it!

211
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:48,279
Okay!

212
00:21:58,019 --> 00:22:00,519
- Get him to the emergency room quickly!
- All right!

213
00:22:05,559 --> 00:22:07,630
What were you doing? He almost died!

214
00:22:07,799 --> 00:22:10,400
You lunatic, all of us could've died
because of you!

215
00:22:10,470 --> 00:22:11,569
Please calm down.

216
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:14,369
It wasn't easy for us to open the door
in these circumstances as well!

217
00:22:18,339 --> 00:22:19,740
I'm sorry.

218
00:22:22,450 --> 00:22:24,720
Follow me, you should get treated too.

219
00:22:24,779 --> 00:22:27,279
Doctor, what are you doing?

220
00:22:28,390 --> 00:22:30,549
If he's bit by an infected,

221
00:22:30,619 --> 00:22:32,059
he's infected as well!

222
00:22:36,029 --> 00:22:37,890
You don't get infected
just from being bit.

223
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:39,460
I'll take responsibility.

224
00:22:39,660 --> 00:22:40,829
Let's go.

225
00:23:05,690 --> 00:23:07,119
You remember me, right?

226
00:23:08,630 --> 00:23:10,029
Yesterday in front of the hospital,

227
00:23:10,089 --> 00:23:12,400
you told me to block out the smoke.

228
00:23:14,700 --> 00:23:15,769
Right.

229
00:23:15,970 --> 00:23:18,640
Thanks to you,
the patients and the people here...

230
00:23:18,700 --> 00:23:20,500
were able to survive.

231
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,240
Thank you.

232
00:23:23,140 --> 00:23:24,240
Take a rest.

233
00:23:24,470 --> 00:23:25,839
Your arm.

234
00:23:27,509 --> 00:23:28,710
Sorry about that.

235
00:23:32,619 --> 00:23:33,619
Sure.

236
00:23:55,839 --> 00:23:58,880
You're free to choose your own destiny.

237
00:23:59,410 --> 00:24:02,250
But you don't have the right
to choose what's good for Do Yoon.

238
00:24:02,980 --> 00:24:04,079
Do Yoon...

239
00:24:04,650 --> 00:24:07,180
is safer here with me.

240
00:24:08,589 --> 00:24:09,920
Think about it.

241
00:24:13,460 --> 00:24:14,559
Detective?

242
00:24:15,390 --> 00:24:16,589
Detective, can you hear me?

243
00:24:21,829 --> 00:24:23,000
Yes, I can hear you.

244
00:24:24,170 --> 00:24:25,839
Thank goodness. You're safe.

245
00:24:27,069 --> 00:24:29,210
Yes. You must be safe too.

246
00:24:29,809 --> 00:24:33,240
Did you... Did you save the kid?

247
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:44,289
Yes, I did,

248
00:24:45,160 --> 00:24:47,289
but I couldn't save the nurse.

249
00:24:48,019 --> 00:24:49,029
I also...

250
00:24:50,430 --> 00:24:52,259
couldn't save my friend.

251
00:24:53,529 --> 00:24:54,900
Don't blame yourself.

252
00:24:55,630 --> 00:24:57,130
It's not your fault.

253
00:24:58,299 --> 00:24:59,299
Where are you?

254
00:25:00,170 --> 00:25:02,710
I'm taking shelter somewhere safe for now.

255
00:25:02,769 --> 00:25:04,140
Where are you?

256
00:25:04,210 --> 00:25:07,380
I'm at Muji Hospital.

257
00:25:07,440 --> 00:25:09,210
Are there any survivors there?

258
00:25:09,910 --> 00:25:11,549
Fortunately, yes.

259
00:25:12,420 --> 00:25:13,519
I see.

260
00:25:14,319 --> 00:25:16,349
I think I should get to the school.

261
00:25:16,420 --> 00:25:18,049
They have a shelter.

262
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:20,960
I'll contact you again.

263
00:25:26,329 --> 00:25:27,329
Please be careful.

264
00:25:32,269 --> 00:25:34,640
I'm giving you an antibiotic
and a tetanus shot.

265
00:25:36,039 --> 00:25:37,039
Okay.

266
00:25:44,849 --> 00:25:46,980
(Nurse Yoon Saet Byeol)

267
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:49,720
- Yoon Saet Byeol.
- From the town?

268
00:25:49,789 --> 00:25:50,950
- From Seoul.
- Age?

269
00:25:51,019 --> 00:25:52,119
22.

270
00:25:53,390 --> 00:25:54,390
Occupation.

271
00:25:55,289 --> 00:25:57,059
What is this, are you interrogating me?

272
