00:48:50,670 --> 00:48:53,539
There's nothing you can do for this child.

537
00:48:54,440 --> 00:48:56,440
Just leave her so Do Yoon can be saved.

538
00:48:56,469 --> 00:48:57,809
Stop talking gibberish.

539
00:48:58,340 --> 00:49:00,280
This isn't salvation, this is murder!

540
00:49:03,079 --> 00:49:05,079
Shut it, you evil!

541
00:49:07,719 --> 00:49:10,320
Do Yoon, drink up.

542
00:49:16,659 --> 00:49:18,059
This is my last warning.

543
00:49:18,730 --> 00:49:19,730
Detective.

544
00:49:22,329 --> 00:49:23,829
Do you still not get it?

545
00:49:24,730 --> 00:49:26,969
The world is coming to its end.

546
00:49:27,039 --> 00:49:28,170
Before it's too late,

547
00:49:28,599 --> 00:49:31,409
let's board the ship of salvation with us.

548
00:49:31,469 --> 00:49:33,010
Stop with your nonsense!

549
00:49:34,110 --> 00:49:37,579
Then shall we let her decide?

550
00:49:37,980 --> 00:49:41,050
Let's ask if she really wants
to stay with you...

551
00:49:41,449 --> 00:49:43,920
in this world that's ending.

552
00:49:45,289 --> 00:49:47,420
Do Yoon, do you...

553
00:49:48,159 --> 00:49:50,389
really not want to see your mom?

554
00:49:50,989 --> 00:49:51,989
Mom.

555
00:49:53,599 --> 00:49:55,199
I miss her.

556
00:49:56,099 --> 00:49:57,829
Then would you like to go with us,

557
00:49:58,199 --> 00:50:00,800
or stay with that lady?

558
00:50:03,840 --> 00:50:04,840
Kid.

559
00:50:05,769 --> 00:50:06,880
Come to me.

560
00:50:07,539 --> 00:50:09,309
Your mom told me to protect you.

561
00:50:10,610 --> 00:50:12,650
Please let me keep that promise.

562
00:50:13,820 --> 00:50:16,179
Do Yoon. Hurry up.

563
00:50:30,469 --> 00:50:31,530
Do Yoon.

564
00:50:33,639 --> 00:50:35,099
Come to me.

565
00:51:12,869 --> 00:51:15,579
How dare you get in the way
of the New Lord's plan?

566
00:51:16,110 --> 00:51:17,280
Run away, now!

567
00:52:54,739 --> 00:52:57,679
4 times 4 is 16. 4 times 5 is 20.

568
00:52:59,309 --> 00:53:02,780
4 times 6 is 24. 4 times 7 is 28.

569
00:53:02,920 --> 00:53:04,750
- Kid.
- 4 times 8 is 3...

570
00:53:05,090 --> 00:53:06,389
Where are you?

571
00:53:14,599 --> 00:53:16,329
My mom...

572
00:53:16,969 --> 00:53:20,469
always found me wherever I hid.

573
00:53:22,300 --> 00:53:23,869
There you are!

574
00:53:23,940 --> 00:53:27,280
Did you think I wouldn't find you
if you hid here?

575
00:53:27,340 --> 00:53:29,949
Mom, how did you know I was here?

576
00:53:30,079 --> 00:53:31,610
I found you with your smell.

577
00:53:31,679 --> 00:53:34,920
It's not a bad smell.
It's a really nice smell.

578
00:53:34,980 --> 00:53:37,789
Do Yoon! Jung Do Yoon!

579
00:53:42,059 --> 00:53:43,119
Mom!

580
00:53:43,789 --> 00:53:47,059
Do Yoon! Are you all right? Are you hurt?

581
00:53:47,099 --> 00:53:48,599
I'm fine.

582
00:53:48,760 --> 00:53:50,269
My baby.

583
00:53:52,369 --> 00:53:56,670
She said she could find me
because I have a nice smell.

584
00:54:04,250 --> 00:54:05,750
It's okay now.

585
00:54:13,760 --> 00:54:16,730
My mom trusted you.

586
00:54:18,289 --> 00:54:20,300
So I trust you too.

587
00:54:31,170 --> 00:54:32,769
We need to get out of here.

588
00:54:34,340 --> 00:54:35,440
Let's go.

589
00:54:59,699 --> 00:55:00,769
(Emergency equipment)

590
00:55:32,829 --> 00:55:35,369
Please forgive my sins.

591
00:55:35,440 --> 00:55:38,440
Please forgive me for what I have sinned!

592
00:55:49,619 --> 00:55:52,289
Go away. I said, go away.

593
00:55:52,349 --> 00:55:55,519
You evil!

594
00:55:55,590 --> 00:55:58,559
Go away! Step back!

595
00:55:59,360 --> 00:56:02,199
I command in the name of the New Lord!

596
00:56:02,360 --> 00:56:04,000
Go away!

597
00:56:04,829 --> 00:56:07,269
Go away!

598
00:56:07,340 --> 00:56:10,869
(Muji Hospital)

599
00:56:21,019 --> 00:56:22,179
Excuse me.

600
00:56:25,449 --> 00:56:26,690
What now?

601
00:56:27,719 --> 00:56:30,590
You got bitten by an infected, didn't you?

602
00:56:30,730 --> 00:56:31,829
A variant?

603
00:56:32,230 --> 00:56:34,829
That's what we call people
whose eyes turned black.

604
00:56:34,929 --> 00:56:37,300
Don't change the topic.
Roll up your sleeve.

605
00:56:37,369 --> 00:56:38,500
Why should I?

606
00:56:39,230 --> 00:56:40,699
I was right.

607
00:56:40,769 --> 00:56:42,570
Officer Cho, handcuff him right now.

608
00:56:46,239 --> 00:56:48,980
- Soon Il, this is enough.
- What are you doing?

609
00:56:49,039 --> 00:56:51,809
You're abusing your authority.
Don't you know that?

610
00:56:52,449 --> 00:56:54,150
I'm not abusing my authority.

611
00:56:54,219 --> 00:56:56,889
It's my job to protect the citizens.

612
00:56:57,090 --> 00:56:58,219
Let me go.

613
00:57:00,360 --> 00:57:03,019
Doctor, you need to see this.

614
00:57:03,090 --> 00:57:05,489
- What happened?
- There's a survivor.

615
00:57:05,889 --> 00:57:07,699
What? Where?

616
00:57:07,760 --> 00:57:09,400
The lab on the fifth floor.

617
00:57:15,639 --> 00:57:17,409
There's a survivor?

618
00:57:21,309 --> 00:57:23,280
Look at that. It's there.

619
00:57:24,250 --> 00:57:26,579
The surgical ward was shut down.

620
00:57:30,519 --> 00:57:32,590
(Help! There are survivors here!)

621
00:57:32,619 --> 00:57:33,889
Wait a minute.

622
00:57:39,989 --> 00:57:42,360
Isn't that your wife?

623
00:57:47,239 --> 00:57:50,039
Baby, Daddy is off to work.
I'll be back soon.

624
00:57:51,440 --> 00:57:52,809
Have a good day!

625
00:57:54,179 --> 00:57:55,510
That's my wife.

626
00:57:55,710 --> 00:57:58,110
Ji Hye is in there!

627
00:59:48,059 --> 00:59:49,190
Hwa Seon!

628
01:00:01,000 --> 01:00:02,070
Hwa Seon!

629
01:00:03,300 --> 01:00:04,409
Hwa Seon!

630
01:00:42,980 --> 01:00:44,550
(We'd like to thank Jung Hae Kyun
for his special appearance.)

631
01:01:03,000 --> 01:01:05,400
(Dark Hole)

632
01:01:05,469 --> 01:01:06,630
Don't lie!

633
01:01:06,699 --> 01:01:09,199
You know no one is coming to save us.

634
01:01:09,269 --> 01:01:10,869
What do you think you're doing?

635
01:01:10,940 --> 01:01:13,510
We can't have everyone here infected!

636
01:01:14,010 --> 01:01:15,909
The pregnant woman is in bad condition.

637
01:01:15,980 --> 01:01:19,010
Sacrifice is needed to save everyone else!

638
01:01:19,079 --> 01:01:21,849
Would you have said that
if they were your family?

639
01:01:21,920 --> 01:01:22,949
Hwa Seon!

640
01:01:23,019 --> 01:01:24,590
They're controlled by someone.

641
01:01:24,619 --> 01:01:26,849
Please open the door.

642
01:01:28,059 --> 01:01:30,219
The black smoke isn't the end of it.
